=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d308f3c10dda9b5477f5ddf82370d282a56a354","tid":1815610,"uid":218871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:53:14.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ab90aa3ab776df992cd0c1654da21634e6550c88","tid":1815610,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T17:00:16.000Z","msg":"呢個好難做到架啦 講真 咁多年加埋條數肯定亂到仆街 verfify唔到<br />\n<br />\n我地都想做到秋後算帳 但目前想做同實踐係兩回事...實踐方面太難做到<br />\n<br />\n咁多素人, 好多野佢地仲學習緊。反而我認為佢地要盡快分時間搞文宣 (地區連儂牆 / 遊行 / 街站介紹工會/ 登記選民 etc)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw,<br />\n請盡快令新勢力成形，被捕人士等唔切呀<br />\n要有具影響力既勢力出現先可以救到手足同香港<br />\n<br />\n工會 &gt; 工會聯盟 , 配合黃色經濟圈。有效咁打經濟同國際戰線<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，同意與否，請聽我一言，睇哂佢，Spread出去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1812233/page/1#preview\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1812233/page/1#preview</a><br />\n<br />\n我P牌推唔到 唯有咁樣推比大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7944f9feda410b294eb3234b4f7469476ca8b112","tid":1815610,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T17:09:34.000Z","msg":"搵同區黃色議員幫手"},{"pid":"78691a8b312ca542349671e175d61a75c7d87512","tid":1815610,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T04:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}